    excerpt: "The lunch rush hits at 12:30 PM. Every table is full, the kitchen is overwhelmed, and three customers are waiting at the door. Sound familiar? Here's how to turn rush hour chaos into smooth, profitable service.",
    author: defaultAuthor,
