    metaDescription: "Complete cloud kitchen business plan for India 2026. Step-by-step guide: concept, licenses, equipment, menu, aggregator onboarding. Startup cost breakdown Ōé╣2-5 lakhs. Start today.",
    excerpt: "Cloud kitchens are the fastest-growing restaurant format in India ŌĆö and you can start one for under Ōé╣5 lakhs. Here's the complete business plan, from concept to first 100 orders.",
    author: defaultAuthor,
