    excerpt: "Zomato and Swiggy are taking 18-30% of every delivery order. On Ōé╣10 lakh monthly delivery revenue, that's Ōé╣1.8-3 lakh going to aggregators every month. Here's how to fight back ŌĆö strategically.",
